NBA宣布暂时停赛。
The NBA suspended the game.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃讯12日，据美国媒体The Athletic记者Shams报道，消息人士透露称，NBA犹他爵士队全明星中锋、两届NBA最佳防守球员鲁迪·戈贝尔的新冠病毒检测呈阳性。
The NBA Utah Jazz All-Star Center and two-time NBA best defender Rudy Goebbels tested positive for the new crown virus, sources said, according to The Athletic reporter Shams.
戈贝尔。
Goebbels.
随后，NBA官方确认了事件的真实性。
Subsequently, NBA officials confirmed the truth of the incident.
而据消息人士透露，戈贝尔感觉良好，情况稳定，身体状况甚至还可以参加今天对雷霆的比赛。
According to the source, Goebbels feels fine, is in stable condition and can even play in today's match against Thunder.
此外，在11日的采访结束后，戈贝尔曾故意用手触碰了自己面前的每一个麦克风和录音设备……鉴于目前的严峻形势，出于安全考虑，NBA已宣布暂停本赛季，何时复赛将另行通知。
In addition, Goebbels had deliberately touched every microphone and recording device in front of him after the interview on the 11th... In view of the current critical situation, the NBA has suspended the season for security reasons until further notice.
而在12日早些时候，根据NBA记者Zach Lowe报道，联盟办公室与董事会的各球队老板在电话会议中达成共识，联盟将选择按原定赛程继续本赛季，让球队空场比赛。
Earlier in the day, NBA correspondent Zach Lowe reported that the league office had reached a consensus in a conference call with board owners that the league would continue this season on its original schedule, leaving the team open.
不过，在NBA联盟决定前，金州勇士队已决定空场。
However, before the NBA decided, the Golden State Warriors had decided not to play.
旧金山市12日宣布在至少两周内禁止1000人以上的聚集性活动，勇士官方也发表声明响应：“由于对新冠疫情扩大的担忧不断加深，在咨询了旧金山市政府的意见后，勇士与本周五主场对阵篮网的比赛将空场进行。
The city of San Francisco on Friday banned more than 1,000 people from gathering for at least two weeks, and the Warrior official response: "With growing concern about the new crown spreading, the Warriors' home game against Nets on Friday, after consulting the San Francisco municipal government, will be vacant.
除此之外，3月21日前的大通中心的所有活动都将延期或取消，球队将给持有期间比赛球票的球迷全额退款。
In addition, all activities at the Chase Center until March 21 will be postponed or cancelled and will be refunded in full to the fans who hold the tickets during the game.
”“球队将继续密切关注疫情的发展情况，以决定对于之后比赛和活动的安排。
"The team will continue to monitor the situation closely to determine the arrangements for the games and activities that will follow.
球队感谢球迷、观众以及合作伙伴在这一前所未有的时期所表现出的理解和耐心。
The team would like to thank the fans, the spectators and the partners for their understanding and patience during this unprecedented period.
”本期编辑 邢潭推荐阅读。
